file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: OpenApi Petstore
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: /v1
tags:
  - name: pets
    description: Pets Tag
  - name: list
    description: List Tag
security:
- petstore_auth:
  - write:pets
  - read:pets
- user_auth:
  - read:user

paths:
  /pets:
    get:
      summary: List all pets
      description: Show a list of pets in the system
      operationId: listPets
      parameters:
        - name: limit
          in: query
          description: How many items to return at one time (max 100)
          required: false
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
      responses:
        '200':
          description: An paged array of pets
